    "entryPoints": [
        {
            "type": "scripts.entryPoint",
            "id": "601aa7bf-9aab-4f3d-a4bf-2bb56128c5c8",
            "name": "Main",
            "nodes": [
                {
                    "type": "nodes.showCloseUp",
                    "imageName": "TapestryPanel2.png"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.showMenu",
                    "id": "49255efb-1b5b-42e2-b6f7-296fcf743347",
                    "options": [
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "3a683bc6-b00a-4b3d-a49c-46d582f37fb3",
                            "text": "Look at the Tapestry",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "18516870-68fc-4528-aa4c-88468b5a9a0b",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "This... this tapestry... it looks like it is telling some sort of story.",
                                    "emotion": "4",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": true,
                            "minutes": 0,
                            "ExitMenu": false
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "fd445462-f476-493e-a467-180f8987c973",
                            "text": "Interpret the Tapestry",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.branch",
                                    "sections": [
                                        {
                                            "type": "nodes.branchSection",
                                            "expression": {
                                                "type": "expressions.inTags",
                                                "scope": "prop",
                                                "scopeId": "26c573b1-14df-4163-88ff-4fc9944391e8",
                                                "scopeFilterId": "981ec865-3e1b-4f3e-bb0d-11df2bc7d593",
                                                "tags": "read4",
                                                "has": true
                                            },
                                            "nodes": [
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "9dca8cb9-a8c5-4290-a488-8a98e45c9fa2",
                                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "actorId2": null,
                                                    "text": "This has got to be the second part of the story, the second tapestry, since it doesn't start with the founding of the Illuminari, and it ends with a cliffhanger. ",
                                                    "emotion": "1",
                                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "0ac42744-27a8-4321-9d1e-b4cf0affbb20",
                                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "actorId2": null,
                                                    "text": "The top section looks like it shows how the Illuminari were banished from Albion for all the destruction they caused while fighting the Dark One's monsters. That is <i>so</i> unfair. But I guess the King didn't like it that his son got killed in the fighting.",
                                                    "emotion": "3",
                                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "c5527d94-c388-48fd-b156-d83eeec3f9c9",
                                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "actorId2": null,
                                                    "text": "In this middle part, they're sailing to an island... that would have to be Sardonia. And that's the Illuminari symbol over the castle on the island. ",
                                                    "emotion": "0",
                                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "4d966515-077a-4c84-9b8f-8981841c35e6",
                                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "actorId2": null,
                                                    "text": "So either they were drawn to just that castle, or somebody inside turned on the Illuminari signal! (okay, so maybe there's a little artistic license here...)",
                                                    "emotion": "1",
                                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "6f73d3e1-1fdb-4173-a410-c23c526c69ac",
                                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "actorId2": null,
                                                    "text": "So now, at the bottom, they're fighting another one of the tentacled beasts that the Dark One sent. I'm guessing... those are Sir Hans and Aquino, with Whim carrying Sir Jamus.",
                                                    "emotion": "0",
                                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "2a054a63-99fd-4782-98e1-bf05fd130260",
                                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "actorId2": null,
                                                    "text": "I guess no place was safe from the Dark One, even after the battle in Albion that came before the events shown on this tapestry.",
                                                    "emotion": "2",
                                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                }
                                            ]
                                        },
                                        {
                                            "type": "nodes.branchSection",
                                            "expression": null,
                                            "nodes": [
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "f5514663-22e3-488d-9a56-66ae86bee140",
                                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "actorId2": null,
                                                    "text": "Okay, let's see. looks like a king is ordering a bunch of people to do something. They take a ship to... hey, it's the castle! So they came to Sardonia. Then they all fought a big monster here. ",
                                                    "emotion": "0",
                                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "bd756a3c-e34f-49fd-b23c-cb50a935b0b8",
                                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "actorId2": null,
                                                    "text": "Wonder what happens next?",
                                                    "emotion": "0",
                                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                }
                                            ]
                                        }
                                    ]
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": true,
                            "minutes": "2",
                            "ExitMenu": false
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "3f189ef0-8f6d-4a60-a8b7-6a0a8f0dc533",
                            "text": "Abscond with the Tapestry",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "3b3e8477-4ae5-4404-bc48-b9fbe02eba1a",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "I might get away with stealing this <i>if</i> I had some sort of bag to carry it in so that nobody could spot it and realize what I was doing. ",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "ed776bfc-bc50-4fbc-a862-56bf2706eaab",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "But I don't want to be known as a carpet bagger!",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": true,
                            "minutes": "1",
                            "ExitMenu": false
                        }
                    ],
